  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of BGB-3111 in Relapsed or Refractory Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia/Small Lymphocytic Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-Arm, Open-Label, Multicenter Phase 2 Study to Evaluate Safety and Efficacy of BGB-3111, a Bruton's Tyrosine Kinase (BTK) Inhibitor in Relapsed or Refractory Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia/Small Lymphocytic Lymphoma (CLL/SLL)</official_title>
